<font color="yellow">Oke!</font>

55
00:01:08,980 --> 00:01:10,020
<font color="yellow">Mari kita berdua minum bersama.</font>

56
00:01:10,020 --> 00:01:12,070
<font color="yellow">Enak aja!
Cepat berikan aku makanan!</font>

57
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:12,820
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

58
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:18,320
<font color="yellow">Coba kita lihat isi kulkas.</font>

59
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:22,370
<font color="yellow">Aduh lapar!</font>

60
00:01:37,010 --> 00:01:38,010
<font color="yellow">Bersulang!</font>

61
00:01:38,010 --> 00:01:41,140
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya hari ini
aku harus menahan lapar lagi.</font>

62
00:01:42,390 --> 00:01:44,390
<font color="yellow">Ah, cape deh!</font>

63
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,480
<font color="yellow">Oh ya!</font>

64
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:52,270
<font color="yellow">Aku lupa kalau Bok Gil tidak suka.</font>

65
00:01:52,610 --> 00:01:53,570
<font color="yellow">Anu, tunggu sebentar!</font>

66
00:01:53,570 --> 00:01:54,400
<font color="yellow">Itu...</font>

67
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:54,980
<font color="yellow">Eh?</font>

68
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:57,240
<font color="yellow">Makan apa?</font>

69
00:01:57,990 --> 00:02:00,160
<font color="yellow">Assa! Udang!</font>

70
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:05,040
<font color="yellow">Sabar ya.</font>

71
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:13,040
<font color="yellow">Sialan, kenapa tidak bisa dibuka?</font>

72
00:02:15,550 --> 00:02:17,340
<font color="yellow">Hei! Hei!</font>

73
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,590
<font color="yellow">Tidur?</font>

74
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:19,800
<font color="yellow">Hei!</font>

75
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,680
<font color="yellow">Jangan!</font>

76
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:26,470
<font color="yellow">Ah, udangku.</font>

77
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,620
<font color="yellow">Bok Gil...</font>

78
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,950
<font color="yellow">Esok akan lebih baik.</font>

79
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:54,960
<font color="yellow">Beritahu aku jika akan membaik.</font>

80
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:57,880
<font color="yellow">Akan membaik.</font>

81
00:03:05,140 --> 00:03:06,850
<font color="yellow">Hei, manusia...</font>

82
00:03:07,390 --> 00:03:11,020
<font color="yellow">Apa yang terjadi sebenarnya hari ini?</font>

83
