<font color="yellow">Kau baca buku?</font>

142
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:49,920
<font color="yellow">Hei! Minatku adalah membaca.</font>

143
00:07:50,090 --> 00:07:51,670
<font color="yellow">Baru kemarin aku baca buku.</font>

144
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,260
<font color="yellow">Judul bukunya adalah...</font>

145
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:56,510
<font color="yellow">Omo! Siapa ini gerangan?</font>

146
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:59,180
<font color="yellow">Raja webtoon kita, komikus Park Jin Seong.</font>

147
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:03,020
<font color="yellow">Dok Goo PD-nim, Anda bilang ingin secepatnya melihat
