148
00:08:03,230 --> 00:08:04,940
<font color="yellow">Kenapa datang secara pribadi?</font>

149
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:06,360
<font color="yellow">Rancangan rencana bisnis yang berharga itu,</font>

150
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:08,650
<font color="yellow">akan kami undang secara khusus.</font>

151
00:08:10,530 --> 00:08:12,570
<font color="yellow">Tapi, kalian berdua saling kenal?</font>

152
00:08:12,610 --> 00:08:13,400
<font color="yellow">- Tidak.
- Iya.</font>

153
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:19,660
<font color="yellow">Berantem?</font>

154
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:21,330
<font color="yellow">Sampai jumpa.</font>

155
00:08:24,250 --> 00:08:27,380
<font color="yellow">Benar-benar danhobak.
<font color=#ffff00>[Danhobak - labu manis]</font></font>

156
00:08:28,130 --> 00:08:32,420
<font color="yellow">Pasti akan sangat lelah
jika harus menangani orang ini.</font>

157
00:08:32,970 --> 00:08:35,380
<font color="yellow">Tabiat kunyuk satu ini jelek sekali.</font>

158
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,840
<font color="yellow">Iya tuh!</font>

159
00:08:37,010 --> 00:08:38,550
<font color="yellow">Seperti itu.</font>

160
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,430
<font color="yellow">Makanya aku sangat tertarik.</font>

161
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:44,560
<font color="yellow">Ingin mencoba membuatnya menjadi sukses.</font>

162
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,810
<font color="yellow">Anu...</font>

163
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,440
<font color="yellow">Bagus sekali.</font>

164
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,780
<font color="yellow">Tuan pekerja paruh waktu yang agung.</font>

165
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:54,070
<font color="yellow">Hanya seeorang pekerja paruh waktu
